---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Contact from "../components/Contact.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import headshotImage from "../assets/tdeveney_headshot_500.jpg";
import slateCertifiedBadge from "../assets/slate_certified.png";
---

<style is:global>
    @import "../styles/global.css";
</style>

<Layout
    title="Slate Consulting and Support | Predicate Higher Ed"
    description="Predicate Higher Ed helps lean Slate teams save time, supplement their in-house capabilities, and build confidence in the accuracy of their dataâ€“all to better serve students. "
>
    <Header />
    <main>
        <section class="page-hero fade-in">
            <div class="narrow-container">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <div class="narrow-container">
                <div class="article-content">
                    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> September 3, 2025</p>

                    <p>
                        This Privacy Policy describes how Predicate Higher Ed
                        LLC ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and shares
                        information when you use our website,
                        predicatehighered.com (the "Site").
                    </p>

                    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We collect information in the following ways:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Information You Provide to Us:</strong> When
                            you fill out our contact form, we collect the personal
                            information you provide, such as your name, email address,
                            job title, institution, and the content of your message.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Information Collected Automatically:</strong
                            > To protect our Site from spam and abuse, we use Cloudflare
                            Turnstile. This service may collect technical information
                            from your device and browser to verify that you are human.
                            We do not use this information for tracking or advertising.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p>
                        We use the information we collect for the following
                        purposes:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            To respond to your inquiries, questions, and
                            comments.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            To provide, operate, and maintain the security of
                            our Site.
                        </li>
                        <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
                    <p>
                        We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may
                        share your information with the following third-party
                        service providers to help us operate our business:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Our Site is hosted on and
                            protected by Cloudflare. Cloudflare may have access to
                            technical data to provide security and hosting services.
                            You can read more in <a
                                href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                >Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a
                            >.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Email Delivery Provider:</strong> When you submit
                            our contact form, your information is processed by our
                            email service provider (Resend) to deliver your message
                            to us.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Data Security</h2>
                    <p>
                        We implement reasonable security measures to help
                        protect your personal information from unauthorized
                        access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of
                        transmission over the Internet is 100% secure, and we
                        cannot guarantee its absolute security.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Cookies</h2>
                    <p>
                        This Site does not use cookies for tracking or analytics
                        purposes, such as Google Analytics. Essential cookies
                        may be used by our third-party service provider,
                        Cloudflare, for security and functionality.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>
                        Depending on your location, you may have certain rights
                        regarding your personal information, such as the right
                        to access, correct, or request the deletion of your
                        data. To make such a request, please contact us at the
                        email address below.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p>
                        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We
                        will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy
                        on this page and updating the "Effective Date" at the
                        top. We encourage you to review this policy
                        periodically.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>
                        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy,
                        please contact us at:<br />
                        info@predicatehighered.com
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
<Footer />
